  "uuid": "7f0c41ce4f4929a12cf2a46f87e8f6e5",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Mortgage Banker",
  "description": "<p>Our client is an international bank and they have a few job openings for the Mortgage Banker position<br /></p><p><br /><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Proactively acquire and activate mortgage loan business. Sales emphasis is on individual residential and commercial loans.</li><li>Establish and maintain relationships with external stakeholders (property agents, brokers) to increase referrals.</li><li>Handle leads from marketing campaigns, inbound inquiries, and branch referrals, engaging both affluent and mass market clients.</li><li>Implement the full mortgage loan application process, responsible for cases up to the customer's acceptance of the offer.</li><li>Offer a wider range of products, including bancassurance and priority banking propositions.</li><li>Keep informed on market trends and competitor offerings, conducting regular updates for target customer groups.</li><li>Ability to work off-office hours and weekends for activities like show flats, campaigns, and networking events.</li><li>Display exemplary conduct and ensure strict compliance with all applicable regulations and the Group's Code of Conduct</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in a related discipline</li><li>2+ years in Banking Sales, preferably with prior experience in Retail Mortgage.</li><li>Strong knowledge of the Singapore Real Estate Market and Mortgage Regulations & Frameworks.</li><li>Good interpersonal skills, stakeholder experience, conversant with and able to work with external partners, and ability to work independently</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Applicants who are keen to apply for this position can send your latest resume to alfred.lai@paradigmrecruitment.com.sg<br /></p><p></p><p>Alfred Lai<br />EA Reg No: R1545971<br />EA License No: 21C0434</p><p><br /></p>",
